videos.headline: McBride airs it out for 40-yard Texas State TD
videos.description: Brady McBride goes deep to Javen Banks to put the Bobcats on the scoreboard first.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (McBride airs it out for 40-yard Texas State TD) 2020/11/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Arkansas State WR makes TD grab with defender all over him
videos.description: Red Wolves WR Jonathan Adams Jr. fights off the defender to catch a touchdown pass while being pulled to the ground.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Arkansas State WR makes TD grab with defender all over him) 2020/11/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Arkansas State WR rips down TD over defender
videos.description: Jonathan Adams Jr. leaps into the air and comes down with the pass for a 30-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Arkansas State WR rips down TD over defender) 2020/11/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Foreman burns defender for 84-yard Arkansas State TD
videos.description: Layne Hatcher connects with Jeff Foreman downfield for an 84-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Foreman burns defender for 84-yard Arkansas State TD) 2020/11/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hill scores late go-ahead TD for Texas State
videos.description: Calvin Hill takes the handoff and finds a hole to give Texas State the lead with less than a minute remaining.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hill scores late go-ahead TD for Texas State) 2020/11/21 ESHEET
